value: Je ne retiens jamais mes coups.
Thank you for this outfit. I will strive to be worthy of it.
*gasp* To let my guard down so easily... I still have much to learn.
Brandir une épée implique que la mort n'est jamais très loin. Je sais bien qu'un jour, mon heure viendra.
Je me demande à quoi ressemble le royaume des morts... La princesse Eir pourra peut-être m'éclairer.
This outfit makes you smile, does it? Well, I do not put much thought into my attire...
Brother... Will I ever catch up to you...?
From this moment on, I will be the sword at your side. Show me who to cut down, and I will bring death upon them.
